Food Truck Face Off - Season 1, Episode 8




Showdown on Wilshire Blvd

Los Angeles is treated to a food truck showdown as two culinary teams compete to win their own food truck for one year. Host Jesse Palmer has the competitors chaotically hustle through rookie mistakes and fryer hazards for their first lunch sell. By Day Two, the teams have to step up their game trying to lure customers away from the established food trucks that line Wilshire Blvd.




Original Air Date: 13-Nov-2014
